        <td width="500" height="18" align="left" valign="top" bgcolor="#993333" class="box_titles">For whom the Deathtolls. <span class="box_titles_small">March 27, 2006, 03:14:29 PM by <a href="mailto:noah@uberyou.com">Noah</a></span>		</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td width="763" align="left" valign="top" bgcolor="#996666" class="box_links">
		<center><br />I'm going to let you in on a little secret on how we got into Deathtoll.  <br /><br /><br /><img src="http://www.fohguild.org/eq2/phpnews/images/gnome.jpg" alt="" style="border:none;" /><br /><br /><br /><br />Yes, thats right.  Straight from the FoH Handbook - Play number 37 -  <b>Sploit Port</b>.   Now, I can't tell you exactly how he did it but here is a screen shot of the kill.   To much of our surprised, Lance came over to congrats us!   <br /><br /><br /><img src="http://www.fohguild.org/eq2/phpnews/images/gore.JPG" alt="" style="border:none;" /><br /><br /><br /><br />With that kill we gained our access to Deathtoll.  On Saturday we entered the most difficult zone EQ2 has to offer.  Of course we all know that monks can solo anything, so with Lonno in the raid - there was little that posed a challenge.  Most of us just watch as he solo'd almost everything in the zone.  Here is a pic of him taking on Amorphous Drake.<br /><br /><br /><img src="http://www.fohguild.org/eq2/gallery/albums/userpics/10016/Amorphous%20Drake.JPG" alt="" style="border:none;" /border=0 width=700 height=525<br /><br /><br />With all kidding aside, Deathtoll is a great looking zone.  It is probably the best art I have seen in EQ2 to date.  God knows we appriciate the fact that this raid zone is original and not just another instance copy of other zones in KOS.  I will say there is definately a lack of excitement to go back due to there only being 5 total named.  At the same time this zone lacks in rewarding you for all the hard work put forth to get in, let alone kill the named.... see for yourself.<br /><br /><a href=http://www.fohguild.org/eq2/gallery/albums/userpics/10088/Talonsreach.jpg>WTF No proc and weak stats?</a> - Grats Kythik.<br /><br /><a href=http://www.fohguild.org/eq2/gallery/albums/userpics/10088/Ashengaze%20Hide%20Jerkin.jpg>I think this rotted....</a> :(<br /><br /><a href=http://www.fohguild.org/eq2/gallery/albums/userpics/10088/Feathered%20Circlet%20of%20Acumen.jpg>Thats right, fuck Bruisers </a> - Grats random 1 100.<br /><br />Here is a stock of <a href=http://www.fohguild.org/eq2/gallery/thumbnails.php?album=8>uber loots </a> we have obtained since KoS release. <br /><br /><br /><center><br /><br />QUOTES QUOTES QUOTES<br />(fuck making them look pretty)<br /><br /><br /><img src="http://www.fohguild.org/eq2/gallery/albums/userpics/10016/kyth%20mt.jpg" alt="" style="border:none;" /><br /><br /><img src="http://www.fohguild.org/eq2/gallery/albums/userpics/10016/fun.JPG" alt="" style="border:none;" /><br /><br /><img src="http://www.fohguild.org/eq2/gallery/albums/userpics/10016/Quotes.JPG" alt="" style="border:none;" /><br /><br /><img src="http://www.fohguild.org/eq2/gallery/albums/userpics/10016/ss.JPG" alt="" style="border:none;" /><br /><br /><img src="http://www.fohguild.org/eq2/gallery/albums/userpics/10016/Insognito-APM.jpg" alt="" style="border:none;" /> </center><br /><br /><b> Insognito's Kick of the Week </b><br /><br /><br /><img src="http://www.fohguild.org/eq2/phpnews/images/firefox.JPG" alt="" style="border:none;" />
		<p>  :: <a href="/eq2/index.php?action=fullnews&amp;showcomments=1&amp;id=22">Comments (5)</a> ::  
[<a href="#top">top</a>]</p>			
		</td>
      </tr>
