        <td width="500" height="18" align="left" valign="top" bgcolor="#993333" class="box_titles">World Wide 1st <span class="box_titles_small">January 12, 2006, 09:30:37 PM by <a href="mailto:noah@uberyou.com">Noah</a></span>		</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td width="763" align="left" valign="top" bgcolor="#996666" class="box_links">
		Last few weeks we have been busy clearing Gates, Court, PPR and FoL.  After weeks of gearing up we finally tackled one of the hardests scripts in EQ2.  <br /><center><br />Pedistal of Sky.<br /></center><br /><br /><A HREF="http://www.fohguild.org/eq2/gallery/albums/userpics/10088/treasure%20of%20sky.jpg"><img src=http://www.fohguild.org/eq2/gallery/albums/userpics/10088/treasure%20of%20sky.jpg border=0 width=800 height=625></A></center><br /><br /><center><br />And yes... the loot was good.<br /><br /><br /><A HREF="http://www.fohguild.org/eq2/gallery/albums/userpics/10088/draconic%20fighting%20baton.jpg"><img src=http://www.fohguild.org/eq2/gallery/albums/userpics/10088/draconic%20fighting%20baton.jpg></A><br /><br /><A HREF="http://www.fohguild.org/eq2/gallery/albums/userpics/10088/dragon%20tooth%20earring.jpg"><img src=http://www.fohguild.org/eq2/gallery/albums/userpics/10088/dragon%20tooth%20earring.jpg></A> </center><br /><br />-Noah
