        <td width="500" height="18" align="left" valign="top" bgcolor="#993333" class="box_titles">In the face!! <span class="box_titles_small">December 16, 2005, 10:16:48 AM by <a href="mailto:noah@uberyou.com">Noah</a></span>		</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td width="763" align="left" valign="top" bgcolor="#996666" class="box_links">
		<b>Operation: Fucking Just Kill It</b> went into effect last night at approximately 00:30 hours.  Details of this mission are very scattered but one brave photographer, Kythik The'Hardcore,  was hot on their trail as <b>Operation:FJKI</b> jumped into action assassinating the Jura Nata, Prime Minister of Cockblockingweakguilds.<br /><br /><A HREF="http://www.fohguild.org/eq2/gallery/albums/userpics/10088/normal_juranata.jpg"><img src=http://www.fohguild.org/eq2/gallery/albums/userpics/10088/normal_juranata.jpg border=0 width=700 height=525></A></center><br /><br />Kythik reports the team continued forward quickly.  Soon to be met up with Captain Cut/Paste - Zaykala!  Only mere minutes passed and Zaykala was executed by the covert team.<br /><br /><A HREF="http://www.fohguild.org/eq2/gallery/albums/userpics/10088/normal_zaykala.jpg"><img src=http://www.fohguild.org/eq2/gallery/albums/userpics/10088/normal_zaykala.jpg border=0 width=700 height=525></A></center><br /><br /><br />An additional photo was found taken by satellite.  <b>Operation: Fucking Just Kill It</b> is seen here in deep negotiations with General Lathena, the last remaining Djinn of the palace.  Reports have come in that Lathena was also killed for violation of Copyright Laws.<br /><br /><A HREF="http://www.fohguild.org/eq2/gallery/albums/userpics/10016/normal_Lathena.JPG"><img src=http://www.fohguild.org/eq2/gallery/albums/userpics/10016/normal_Lathena.JPG border=0 width=700 height=525></A></center><br /><br /><br />The Loots:<br /><a href=http://www.fohguild.org/eq2/gallery/albums/userpics/10088/force%20wrapped%20plate%20boots.jpg>Jizz Boots of Noah Whoring</a>.<br /><a href=http://www.fohguild.org/eq2/gallery/albums/userpics/10088/cord%20of%20shimmering%20essence.jpg>the rune of hek</a>. <br /><a href=http://www.fohguild.org/eq2/gallery/albums/userpics/10088/sun%20emblazoned%20chestplate.jpg>Please add scout loot with Str and good DW weapons with effects so they stop bitching at raids</a>.
		<p>  :: <a href="/eq2/index.php?action=fullnews&amp;showcomments=1&amp;id=19">Comments (5)</a> ::  
[<a href="#top">top</a>]</p>			
		</td>
      </tr>
