        <td width="500" height="18" align="left" valign="top" bgcolor="#993333" class="box_titles">So long, farewell, auf wiedersehen...... <span class="box_titles_small">December 14, 2005, 02:16:51 PM by <a href="mailto:noah@uberyou.com">Noah</a></span>		</td>
      </tr>
      <tr>
        <td width="763" align="left" valign="top" bgcolor="#996666" class="box_links">
		Its been an interesting 2 weeks.  First, I want to thank the following <a href=http://wcr.us/noah/mdu/Quotes/disbanding.jpg>people</a>.  Some of you I will miss but most will be thought as splinters finally removed from the bottom of my foot.<br /><br />This action caused "Operation: Find Some Fuckers That Don't Suck" to spring into action.  Drafting about 8 quality players (IE: non-AFKrs, people that listen, and non whiners), Operation: FSFTDS was a complete success in creating a crack team that destroys anything in its path.  Upkeeping with tradition of FoH owning server 1st... our revamped team accomplished more in the past 7 days than in the previous 2 months.<br /><br /><b>Rheon</b><br /><A HREF="http://wcr.us/noah/mdu/Rheon.JPG"><img src=http://wcr.us/noah/mdu/Rheon.JPG border=0 width=700 height=525></A></center><br /><br /><b>Sunchild</b><br /><A HREF="http://wcr.us/noah/mdu/sunchild.jpg"><img src=http://wcr.us/noah/mdu/sunchild.jpg border=0 width=700 height=525></A></center><br /><br /><br />With luck on our side we had a chance to kill this guy "in the face" as well.<br /><br /><b>Xideus Yoatiak</b><br /><A HREF="http://wcr.us/noah/mdu/Gargoyal.JPG"><img src=http://wcr.us/noah/mdu/Gargoyal.JPG border=0 width=700 height=525></A></center><br /><br /><br />To round out the past week we enjoyed downing Barakah in PoF, Captain in FoL, Terror (SS1,2 and 3... thx bot farmers!), clearing Court, and getting up to Juanita in Poetsx4.  Everyone adjusted great to the roster changes and soon Godking / Juanita will fall and give us crappy loots per the usual.<br /><br /><center><b>OMFG WHAT DROPPED?!?!?</b><br />A select few of our finest that we procured.</center><br /><center><br /><br /><img src="http://www.fohguild.org/eq2/phpnews/images/circlet of living fire.jpg" alt="" /><br /><br /><img src="http://www.fohguild.org/eq2/phpnews/images/tunic of the mystic.jpg" alt="" /><br /><br /><img src="http://www.fohguild.org/eq2/phpnews/images/Daywalkers Cowl.jpg" alt="" /><br /><br /><img src="http://www.fohguild.org/eq2/phpnews/images/cold-forged barbute.jpg" alt="" /><br /><br /><img src="http://www.fohguild.org/eq2/phpnews/images/shortsword of sorrow.jpg" alt="" /><br /><br /></center><br /><br />QuotesQuotesQuotes stfukythik (<3 Triton TM).<br /><br /><img src=http://wcr.us/noah/mdu/Quotes/gaige.jpg><br /><br /><img src=http://wcr.us/noah/mdu/Quotes/stella.jpg><br /><br /><img src=http://wcr.us/noah/mdu/Quotes/hagann.jpg><br /><br /><img src=http://wcr.us/noah/mdu/Quotes/kienas.jpg><br /><br /><img src=http://wcr.us/noah/mdu/Quotes/kienas2.jpg><br /><br />How Linyen decides what hand to use<br /><img src=http://wcr.us/noah/mdu/Quotes/Linyen%20hands.JPG><br /><br /><img src=http://wcr.us/noah/mdu/Quotes/marshaa.jpg><br /><br /><img src=http://wcr.us/noah/mdu/Quotes/marsha2.jpg><br /><br /><img src=http://wcr.us/noah/mdu/Quotes/marsha3.jpg><br /><br /><img src=http://wcr.us/noah/mdu/Quotes/noah.jpg><br /><img src=http://wcr.us/noah/mdu/Quotes/mystique.jpg><br /><br /><img src=http://wcr.us/noah/mdu/Quotes/Pathofood.JPG><br /><br /><img src=http://wcr.us/noah/mdu/Quotes/ssin.jpg><br /><br /><img src=http://wcr.us/noah/mdu/Quotes/stilpon.JPG><br /><br /><img src=http://wcr.us/noah/mdu/Quotes/vasel.jpg>
		<p>  :: <a href="/eq2/index.php?action=fullnews&amp;showcomments=1&amp;id=18">Comments (4)</a> ::  
