        <td width="500" height="18" align="left" valign="top" bgcolor="#993333" class="box_titles">Another Server 1st... <span class="box_titles_small">July 01, 2005, 08:41:49 PM by <a href="mailto:noah@uberyou.com">Noah</a></span>		</td>
