        <td width="763" align="left" valign="top" bgcolor="#996666" class="box_links">
		Mr. Mal died to 22 FoH tonight.  I would like to personally thank the designer on this raid - it was pretty pimp.  I am still pretty pissed off about Mal bugging on us the 1st time there and wasting 24 peoples time... When I can, i'll post some nice pics of what happens when you gather 24 bored FoH waiting for a GM response.<br /><br />Great job fellas, once again bringing home the 1st trophy for us.  <br /><br />Till next time something is worth my time to update...<br /><br />Lates,<br /><br />Noah
